CHANGES0009 - Infrastructure for d² and d-preserves-alt

Major changes:
1. Added negPow-suc-cancel: negPow n a + negPow (suc n) a ≡ 0g
   - Simple consequence of +InvR

2. Added face-comp: general face map composition via simplicial identity
   - faceMap j (faceMap i σ) ≡ faceMap i' (faceMap (fsuc j) σ) when fst i ≤ fst j
   - Direct from simplicial via funExt

3. Added sfg-0: sumFinGen of all-zero function is zero
   - By induction on n, using cong₂ and +IdR

4. Added sumFinGen-swap (Fubini): interchange of nested sumFinGen
   - Σᵢ Σⱼ g(i,j) ≡ Σⱼ Σᵢ g(i,j)
   - By induction on n, using IH + sym(sumFinGen-+)
   - Key infrastructure for general d² = 0 proof

Remaining holes: d-preserves-alt (2 holes)
Remaining postulates: d² (general), cπ-homotopic-to-id, contractible-with-section

